# No environment variables are needed here.
#
# The API base URL is always relative (/api/v1) — see src/lib/api.js.
# - In dev, Vite's proxy (vite.config.js) forwards it to localhost:5000.
# - In production, Vercel's rewrite (vercel.json) proxies it to the Render
#   backend, so the frontend and API stay same-origin from the browser's
#   perspective. Do NOT add a VITE_API_URL override — it bypasses the proxy
#   and reintroduces cross-origin CORS/cookie issues.
